About Us







Careers
At Novanta we contribute to building a better world and improve the lives of patients by solving difficult problems with leading global healthcare and advanced manufacturing OEMs. We innovate to solve the most challenging problems using our competences in photonics, vision and motion technologies. Our teams are often the differentiator for our customers, allowing them to make the best performing products and get to market faster.
At the heart of our business we engineer core components and sub-systems that deliver cutting edge precision and performance. We work closely with our customers, listen to their needs and then tailor solutions to solve for their most demanding applications:

We enable submicron motion accuracy and unsurpassed quality in surgical robots, metrology tools or advanced semiconductor equipment used to produce smart phones
In the surgical operating room we help surgeons operate more effectively with improved patient safety by combining minimally invasive surgery technologies with RFID technology.
We provide auto-identification solutions in patient monitoring, blood analysis and point of care applications in the hospital that improve patient safety, clinical outcomes and workflow.
In advanced manufacturing we are providing leading edge accuracy and speed in 3D Printers with our lasers and laser beam delivery products

Novanta is growing and the driving force behind our growth is the team of innovative professionals who share a commitment to innovation and customer success.
If you want to build a meaningful career working with like-minded people that operate with a bias for action and a commitment to solving ever increasing challenges, then you should contact us today to learn about our opportunities.
We are constantly seeking new team members to join us in our mission. Learn about our current open positions →



