Company Profile
Sector: Industrials
Industry: Electrical Equipment
Sub-Industry: Electrical Components
Novanta, Inc. designs, develops, manufactures, and sells precision photonics and motion control components and subsystems. The Company offers its products to original equipment manufactures in the medical equipment and advanced industrial technology markets.




